Instead of 3500 kroner monthly rent, the son is to pay 4100 kroner next year for a 2 bedroom apartment with a second category kitchen.
"And since there is not even running hot water in the apartment and you have to heat in a simple coal stove," he taps with his finger angry at the new lease of the son, for which he has a power of attorney to sign.
"But what - I signed," he explains half disappointed and half resigned.
