The PLM software is capable of analyzing and improving all components of Red Bull’s racing cars, with the exception of the engine, for which Renault is solely responsible.
The materials, fuel, aerodynamics and safety elements are changed.
The changes can be transferred from the virtual reality of the simulator to reality in less than 24 hours thanks to advanced production facilities and high-tech autoclaves.
