Islamabad says nuclear weapons are “faster than any other country”
WikiLeaks reveals ties between the Taliban and Pakistan.
The content of the correspondence between the North American Embassy in Pakistan and the U.S. State Department, revealed by the Wikileaks internet portal, confirms the enormous concerns the Pakistani nuclear program in Washington is causing.
