It’s not new, it’s dated November 20th.
It also has nothing to do with the recent unveiling of over four million U.S. diplomatic documents, but with the accusations of sexual abuse that the Australian faces in Sweden.
WikiLeaks founder Mark Stephens said the police would know where and how to contact Mr. Assange.
